snippet.title: Shredders coming to Xbox Series X|S, Game Pass and Steam!
snippet.description:
Alongside Xbox Series X|S and Game Pass we're stoked to announce that Shredders is coming to Steam! 🏂

Wishlist now! ➡️ https://store.steampowered.com/app/1874170
